OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,FFormer England Under-21s manager Aidy
OL,7,FBoothroyd has revealed he has
OL,8,FParkinson's, having been diagnosed
OL,9,Fduring a routine health check more
OL,10,Fthan three years ago.
OL,12,FThe former Watford boss succeeded
OL,13,FGareth Southgate as England Under-21s
OL,14,Fmanager in 2016 and spent five years
OL,15,Fin the role before leaving in April
OL,16,F2021.
