OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,FIn a statement on the League Managers
OL,7,FAssociation's website on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fthe 54-year-old revealed he was
OL,9,Fdiagnosed in November 2021 following a
OL,10,Fhealth assessment.
OL,12,F"Three years ago, I was diagnosed with
OL,13,FParkinson's. The news came as a
OL,14,Fmassive shock to me, following what I
OL,15,Fexpected to be my routine LMA annual
OL,16,Fhealth assessment," Boothroyd said.
OL,18,F"It has taken me time to feel ready to
OL,19,Fshare my diagnosis, and I have found
OL,20,Fit difficult not being completely open
OL,21,Fwith people.
