OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,F"Personally, my passion and love for
OL,7,Fcoaching is as strong as ever, I am
OL,8,Ffocusing on keeping physically fit,
OL,9,Fwhich is key to slowing down the
OL,10,Fprogression of Parkinson's.
OL,12,F"I am ready to start the next chapter
OL,13,Fin my life. I would like to thank the
OL,14,FLMA and Parkinson's UK for their
OL,15,Fsupport."
