OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,FIn a video released by the LMA,
OL,7,FBoothroyd described how difficult the
OL,8,Flast three years have been, but
OL,9,Fbelieves he now feels more comfortable
OL,10,Fto talk openly about his condition.
OL,12,FHe said: "Psychologically it's been
OL,13,Ftough, physically it's been easier,
OL,14,FI'm coping well with that because I'm
OL,15,Fa former footballer who's worked on
OL,16,Fthe grass every day as a coach, as a
OL,17,Fmanager so that's easy getting up and
OL,18,Fbeing disciplined to go for a run or
OL,19,Fdo some exercise, because exercise is
OL,20,Fthe key thing in staving off this
OL,21,Fcondition.
