OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,F"It's been tough, but now I feel a lot
OL,7,Fmore able to come out and talk about
OL,8,Fthese things."
OL,10,FAfter leaving his England role
OL,11,Ffollowing the team's exit from the
OL,12,FEuropean Under-21 Championship in
OL,13,F2021, Boothroyd had a short spell as
OL,14,Fpart of the Northern Ireland coaching
OL,15,Fstaff in May 2022.
OL,17,FHe added his focus was now on keeping
OL,18,Ffit and bringing more awareness to the
OL,19,Fcondition.
