OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,F"To be honest it's been a burden,
OL,7,Fthree years it's taken me to come to
OL,8,Fthis position," Boothroyd said.
OL,10,F"It is a bit like my life's been on
OL,11,Fhold for all of us, really, for my
OL,12,Ffamily, for my kids and people have
OL,13,Fjust wanted to be helpful and that's
OL,14,Fgreat.
OL,16,F"I don't want to wallow, don't want
OL,17,Fpity, all I want is to get back on the
OL,18,Fpitch or whatever it is I end up doing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@OO]rD@AOUxD@AOU
