OL,3,CEx-England U21s boss reveals
OL,4,CParkinson's diagnosis
OL,6,F"I won't let this define me, I'll
OL,7,Fcontinue, I'll keep fit, I'll do what
OL,8,FI've got to do in the gym and
OL,9,Fhopefully I can get a job with a
OL,10,Fpurpose.
OL,12,F"But for now, it's about getting this
OL,13,Foff my chest and seeing if I can help
OL,14,Fand bring awareness to more people
OL,15,Fabout this condition."
